  "detailed_description": "Help Circuit Dude build his ultimate secret invention by plugging in chips, pushing blocks, stepping on switches, rotating walls and so much more in this game featuring over 15 hours of gameplay over 120 levels. If that's not enough, you can design your own master contraptions using the in-game level editor and even upload it to the internet for others to try out! What is Circuit Dude building? Finish the first 100 levels to find out!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662410/extras/dc13cd3e28d41cffcba18e4fc9bdb352.webp?t=1597168101\" width=32 height=35 /></span> 120 Levels<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662410/extras/799d9d09b1f054216615567a1257a37f.webp?t=1597168101\" width=32 height=35 /></span> 15+ Hours of Puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662410/extras/8bd88448c8bc780c62cc6fe9dc8ad53b.webp?t=1597168101\" width=32 height=35 /></span> 10 Cool Tile Mechanics<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662410/extras/67db37ee198532c448aeb1fbed2ca002.webp?t=1597168101\" width=32 height=35 /></span> Level Editor<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662410/extras/2e553f4b3606709c666283c6a74cbe0b.webp?t=1597168101\" width=32 height=35 /></span> Online Level Sharing<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662410/extras/e4d6ea6c6bb5d81e9b35821024120986.avif?t=1597168101\" width=374 height=180 /></span>",
